OL,5, Racism towards people of African       
OL,6, descent remains "relentless and        
OL,7, pervasive", the European Union Agency  
OL,8, for Fundamental Rights (FRA) has said. 
OL,10,FA survey of black people living in 13  
OL,11,FEU countries found many are subjected  
OL,12,Fto discrimination and violence that    
OL,13,F"continues to haunt their daily lives".
OL,15,FIn Germany, the number of people who   
OL,16,Ffelt discriminated against has almost  
OL,17,Fdoubled since the last survey in 2018. 
OL,19,FThe findings should be "a wake-up      
OL,20,Fcall," the EU agency said.             
